The paper discusses the characteristics and distribution of funding acknowledgment data in Web of Science, which involves information retrieval and analysis. This aligns with several sub-categories in computer science, including digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), cybersecurity (cs.CY), cryptography (cs.CR), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
